<item>
            <title>[LU-12379] write openlock conflicts needlessly with other operations</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12379</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Looks like all the careful logic we had in 1.x releases where all read operations were getting CR locks was lost in 2.x conversion and now whenever we get a CW lock for WRITE openhandle caching, subsequent stats and other such operations would cancel it quickly negating the benefit.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Need to convert most of the locks back to CR mode I guess.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
